MATT: Welcome back. So. Jumping back into the
chaos, the party has scattered back into the

00:25:36.732 --> 00:25:42.191
rainstorm. I would like everyone to make a stealth
check.

00:25:42.191 --> 00:25:43.853
LAURA: Oh, right. Plus ten for everybody.

00:25:43.853 --> 00:25:45.340
MATT: Plus ten.

00:25:45.340 --> 00:25:48.657
LIAM: I did all right.

00:25:48.657 --> 00:25:52.547
TALIESIN: I rolled my disadvantage.

00:25:52.547 --> 00:25:54.819
TRAVIS: Does it matter on a one?

00:25:54.819 --> 00:25:57.180
MATT: All right.

